      "content": "thanks. i tried drinking some water a bit ago but i'm still struggling to talk and it feels like my brain is just foggy and slow. i don't really wanna go to a doctor or a clinic if i can help it, it's just a mess here. do you think i should just take some extra electrolytes and sleep it off? i'm feeling pretty out of it.",
